00:02:46.460 --> 00:02:48.540
to unpick that a little
bit and understand

00:02:48.540 --> 00:02:51.920
what risks you're taking
and then why resilience

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:53.170
is important.

00:02:53.170 --> 00:02:57.000
So in terms of the risks
that people in this room

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.800
