AUDIENCE: Robust.

00:07:01.020 --> 00:07:01.390
PETER READ: Sorry?

00:07:01.390 --> 00:07:02.098
AUDIENCE: Robust.

00:07:02.098 --> 00:07:02.970
PETER READ: Robust.

00:07:02.970 --> 00:07:04.215
It's a great one.

00:07:04.215 --> 00:07:05.673
Sorry, there was
another one there?

00:07:05.673 --> 00:07:06.420
AUDIENCE: Strong.

00:07:06.420 --> 00:07:07.211
PETER READ: Strong.

00:07:07.211 --> 00:07:07.942
Yeah.

00:07:07.942 --> 00:07:08.900
And those are all good.

00:07:08.900 --> 00:07:11.510
And that's exactly where
I started when asked

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:13.000
