SPEAKER 1: Unfortunately, we've
come to the end of our hour

00:56:14.530 --> 00:56:14.720
now.

00:56:14.720 --> 00:56:16.270
But Ruby and Peter,
thank you so--

00:56:16.270 --> 00:56:16.860
RUBY WAX: Thank you.

00:56:16.860 --> 00:56:19.193
SPEAKER 1: --so much for
coming today and talking to us.

